{"tid":292641,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇方法可以搵到首歌既編曲方法？","createTime":"2017-06-21T14:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T13:42:03.000Z","uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"810310b5ed4d2dd7d3d69b7327044a9b339866a0","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"呢排作左d歌，又學緊d音樂程式，諗住自己試下編下自己作個幾首歌，就諗住研究下人地d歌入面用左d咩樂器，但有時聽落入面好似落左好多樂器，尤其周杰倫d歌，<br />\n<br />\n只係知有幾樣好必須同常見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  琴，小提琴，鼓，但入面仲有一d聽唔到認唔到，有冇咩網有呢類知識？或者有冇方法可以知道首歌當中用左咩樂器等？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b14953449c501484b2175a0954522e41ab6494","tid":292641,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:03:35.000Z","msg":"有小提琴好多時都有其他弦樂部份<br />\n仲有結他 percussion <br />\n通常加埋synth 同 pad感覺成首歌會full啲"},{"pid":"7eab0a057b2b23c66c133d545b357a5c3da9cbe2","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有小提琴好多時都有其他弦樂部份<br />\n仲有結他 percussion <br />\n通常加埋synth 同 pad感覺成首歌會full啲</blockquote><br />\n唔加合成器應該做唔到平時聽開既流行曲既水準？ 個分別會係邊？<br />\n<br />\n完全唔知個d mixer synth, 黎緊有時間都想略略研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be356901b1fdca4664e91ec404b1025c7c27290","tid":292641,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:25:37.000Z","msg":"冇錯如果你話流行曲標準的話<br />\n<br />\n有筆直既通常係真假弦樂一齊<br />\n加synth同pad做底<br />\n加埋主要樂器<br />\n分分鐘百幾條trks"},{"pid":"0bb4bb002f34f81ba28de68eeb9eb8165e27227a","tid":292641,"uid":69187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:27:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff88eb8c276afed8d6aba6c06694f39170d210c7","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇錯如果你話流行曲標準的話<br />\n<br />\n有筆直既通常係真假弦樂一齊<br />\n加synth同pad做底<br />\n加埋主要樂器<br />\n分分鐘百幾條trks</blockquote><br />\n百幾條track<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔講唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但一隊band玩live個陣都係可能兩枝結他，一個琴，一個鼓，bass，但出黎個伴奏都ok？ 同cd唔會差太遠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5d0ec3d5a0175b54fdf35851b35dddf57a1aa1","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你用開邊個編曲軟件?<br />\n你可以search下有冇d midi檔  <br />\n成首拖入去個軟件睇下佢有幾多野係首歌入面</blockquote><br />\n其實都係岩岩自學冇耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用緊MacBook pro就用GarageBand 著手先 ，等熟絡左上左手唔夠用先再可能買logic pro ，<br />\n<br />\n佢midi直頭可以有個檔係入落d音樂軟件到睇番d tracks??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4cb36af8bb1e2868f9f233d430d287e127f849","tid":292641,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T01:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇錯如果你話流行曲標準的話<br />\n<br />\n有筆直既通常係真假弦樂一齊<br />\n加synth同pad做底<br />\n加埋主要樂器<br />\n分分鐘百幾條trks</blockquote><br />\n百幾條track<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔講唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但一隊band玩live個陣都係可能兩枝結他，一個琴，一個鼓，bass，但出黎個伴奏都ok？ 同cd唔會差太遠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常live會重新編曲<br />\n大型既有成隊管弦樂backup<br />\n有時有特別效果就有電腦programming現場cue<br />\n電腦電子琴synthesizer 就負責電子編曲材料同synth pad呢啲"},{"pid":"7068c76e5e90e727aee0ecaa24dc805105089f29","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T10:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇錯如果你話流行曲標準的話<br />\n<br />\n有筆直既通常係真假弦樂一齊<br />\n加synth同pad做底<br />\n加埋主要樂器<br />\n分分鐘百幾條trks</blockquote><br />\n百幾條track<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔講唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但一隊band玩live個陣都係可能兩枝結他，一個琴，一個鼓，bass，但出黎個伴奏都ok？ 同cd唔會差太遠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常live會重新編曲<br />\n大型既有成隊管弦樂backup<br />\n有時有特別效果就有電腦programming現場cue<br />\n電腦電子琴synthesizer 就負責電子編曲材料同synth pad呢啲</blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇方法可以搵多d呢類型既資料？或者應該打d咩可以搵到呢d編曲教學片？<br />\n<br />\n用左幾日garageband，自己試下乜都加下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整左一段副歌伴奏都似似到平時聽到既流行曲伴奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔介意我可以貼上黎巴打俾少少意見我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外其實想問一下其實係咪通常常見既流行曲都係慢慢一頭段慢慢中段到副歌慢慢逐步逐步咁加更多樂器上去黎製造愈黎愈full既感覺？<br />\n<br />\n姐係例如我成日大部分用琴彈，到可能中段就加鼓，到副歌就再加埋小提琴，結他咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能問得有d新手，希望可以解答到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該巴打"},{"pid":"3168ee0847dd959fd6ad2a8aea31a2a1ff22360f","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8239209ddea192a2e6c05bf5e42ac1b99b533adf","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6cdc6e6b591bacd7c5eb29765445e86bba5de2","tid":292641,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇錯如果你話流行曲標準的話<br />\n<br />\n有筆直既通常係真假弦樂一齊<br />\n加synth同pad做底<br />\n加埋主要樂器<br />\n分分鐘百幾條trks</blockquote><br />\n百幾條track<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔講唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但一隊band玩live個陣都係可能兩枝結他，一個琴，一個鼓，bass，但出黎個伴奏都ok？ 同cd唔會差太遠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常live會重新編曲<br />\n大型既有成隊管弦樂backup<br />\n有時有特別效果就有電腦programming現場cue<br />\n電腦電子琴synthesizer 就負責電子編曲材料同synth pad呢啲</blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇方法可以搵多d呢類型既資料？或者應該打d咩可以搵到呢d編曲教學片？<br />\n<br />\n用左幾日garageband，自己試下乜都加下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整左一段副歌伴奏都似似到平時聽到既流行曲伴奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔介意我可以貼上黎巴打俾少少意見我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外其實想問一下其實係咪通常常見既流行曲都係慢慢一頭段慢慢中段到副歌慢慢逐步逐步咁加更多樂器上去黎製造愈黎愈full既感覺？<br />\n<br />\n姐係例如我成日大部分用琴彈，到可能中段就加鼓，到副歌就再加埋小提琴，結他咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能問得有d新手，希望可以解答到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該巴打</blockquote><br />\n你試吓search music arrangement<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講得啱 <br />\n流行曲好多係差唔多ABC段咁逐層layer上去<br />\n其實搵教學之餘<br />\n我覺得聽多啲歌最重要<br />\n聽下外國流行歌 聽聽下聽另類一啲嘅<br />\n咁就會知道人哋點做"},{"pid":"932a46c4f87b4e48182e85d89794444670f045ea","tid":292641,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇錯如果你話流行曲標準的話<br />\n<br />\n有筆直既通常係真假弦樂一齊<br />\n加synth同pad做底<br />\n加埋主要樂器<br />\n分分鐘百幾條trks</blockquote><br />\n百幾條track<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔講唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但一隊band玩live個陣都係可能兩枝結他，一個琴，一個鼓，bass，但出黎個伴奏都ok？ 同cd唔會差太遠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常live會重新編曲<br />\n大型既有成隊管弦樂backup<br />\n有時有特別效果就有電腦programming現場cue<br />\n電腦電子琴synthesizer 就負責電子編曲材料同synth pad呢啲</blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇方法可以搵多d呢類型既資料？或者應該打d咩可以搵到呢d編曲教學片？<br />\n<br />\n用左幾日garageband，自己試下乜都加下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整左一段副歌伴奏都似似到平時聽到既流行曲伴奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔介意我可以貼上黎巴打俾少少意見我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外其實想問一下其實係咪通常常見既流行曲都係慢慢一頭段慢慢中段到副歌慢慢逐步逐步咁加更多樂器上去黎製造愈黎愈full既感覺？<br />\n<br />\n姐係例如我成日大部分用琴彈，到可能中段就加鼓，到副歌就再加埋小提琴，結他咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能問得有d新手，希望可以解答到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該巴打</blockquote><br />\n你試吓search music arrangement<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講得啱 <br />\n流行曲好多係差唔多ABC段咁逐層layer上去<br />\n其實搵教學之餘<br />\n我覺得聽多啲歌最重要<br />\n聽下外國流行歌 聽聽下聽另類一啲嘅<br />\n咁就會知道人哋點做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細心啲聽咩樂器<br />\n音樂係要浸淫<br />\n就算平時玩開樂器 <br />\n聽得少歌都係做唔到編曲"},{"pid":"3b95376b1fa7de2391aaf2976dfcd56eda801f91","tid":292641,"uid":78460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:39:55.000Z","msg":"巴打岩岩開始用garageband既話唔好咁衝動買logic啊 慢慢用熟左garageband先 入面有好多野慢慢研究 用左一年幾真係真係覺得好唔夠用先買logic都未遲"},{"pid":"cea15944ea2769dcd2b2acdbcc34845a90194272","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9648dfe47099e55b3f1dc31d94e7b7d1ae3b3503","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271488e3b7cbadf56e3cb9f676f7167c8502c673","tid":292641,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"Hdhcbbc"},{"pid":"4247d0db6c00631c4661a1eb1e7a2081e544eb0d","tid":292641,"uid":7847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T13:08:12.000Z","msg":"放段track上尼聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517c1af6ee638b6041e839685171e6f113cd0461","tid":292641,"uid":118653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"都想學野，自己都研究緊grange band,一齊交流下<img src=\"/as